data.description: This amazing, recently RENOVATED home in the up-and-coming Eastlake community is a must see!  This property has three large bedrooms, one full bath with new fixtures, eat-in kitchen, new floor, new windows, large fenced backyard and a large side porch and back patio, perfect for entertaining or just relaxing in this energized area. This is a quiet neighborhood, very close to Ruffner Mountain, a public golf course, downtown, the airport and several shops.  This area is getting popular quickly, don’t miss seeing this wonderful property. Set an appointment today!!!
